{\listtext	\'95	}1 rib finely chopped celery\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 garlic {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/clove/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 clove}}, minced\
